WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:07.000
Agar aap small business owner hain, home business chalate hain, restaurant ya cloud kitchen manage karte hain, toh IKIGAI aapke liye hai.

00:07.000 --> 00:15.000
IKIGAI aapke digital business tasks ko simple aur organized banaata hai.

00:15.000 --> 00:28.000
Hum WhatsApp Business setup, catalog, product listing, restaurant aur cloud kitchen setup, social media setup, aur website ya online store setup mein help karte hain.

00:28.000 --> 00:38.000
Website use karna simple hai. Get Started par click kijiye, account banaiye, service select kijiye, title aur description likhiye, aur task submit kar dijiye.

00:38.000 --> 00:50.000
Uske baad IKIGAI task review karta hai, usko properly structure karta hai, aur trained IKIGAI Partners ke through kaam complete karwata hai.

00:50.000 --> 01:02.000
Aap apne dashboard mein task status, progress, aur latest updates dekh sakte hain.

01:02.000 --> 01:10.000
Aur agar aap flexible earning karna chahte hain, toh IKIGAI Partner ke roop mein bhi join kar sakte hain. Aaj hi IKIGAI ke saath get started kijiye.
